{"body": "I don't think we have to add it to Inflector. You can easily add it to one of your initializers\r\n\r\n``` ruby\r\nActiveSupport::Inflector.inflections do |inflect|\r\n  inflect.irregular 'criterion', 'criteria'\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\n(If i am not mistaken, inflector is sort of frozen now for such changes. We can't add all possible examples to Rails) //cc @steveklabnik ", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/22613907", "created_at": "2013-08-14T04:07:16Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11876#issuecomment-22613907", "updated_at": "2013-08-14T04:07:57Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11876, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/prathamesh-sonpatki", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/1b0973b64704738dbc8ce24d8382bb1f?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F10a7864f54092aa82b4a41d2f0ec370c.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1b0973b64704738dbc8ce24d8382bb1f", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "prathamesh-sonpatki", "type": "User", "id": 621238, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/prathamesh-sonpatki/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d080bd3543c151007cd0"}, "id": 22613907, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11876"}
